{"tid":1993760,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 黃屍計劃放炸彈！！！","createTime":"2020-04-29T04:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T06:32:41.000Z","uid":67812,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"ab127edc3b7be26cdb0784e2bc4cf736c0db38ff","tid":1993760,"uid":67812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:01:53.000Z","msg":"原來藍c 谷傳緊呢段野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出入坐車時要小心😱<br />\n信不信由你，命只得一條。<br />\n<br />\n網傳香港區金主被補無臉，黃屍港毒要做嘢， 雖然規模會細啲，但會用炸彈。<br />\n<br />\n如見有留低手提袋等等，千祈唔好走近！<br />\n<br />\n另外5 月1 日多留在家中比較安全呀 。<br />\n阿 Sir Madam 個日工作時，多加萬事小心 ！<br />\n<br />\n【 金主命令，黑暴再來，唔比香港有復原的一日 。】 <br />\n<br />\n日期: 5月1日<br />\n<br />\n時間: 中午12時<br />\n<br />\n玩嘢地點: <br />\n<br />\n金鐘港鐵站 A出口 <br />\n<br />\n油麻地港鐵站 A1出口<br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀港鐵站 A1出口<br />\n<br />\n旺角港鐵站 A1出口<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙港鐵站 B1出口<br />\n<br />\n荃灣港鐵站 A出口<br />\n<br />\n沙田新城市廣場<br />\n<br />\n元朗大馬路<br />\n<br />\n屯門大會堂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caaa8efb796af17cbb57efd778755605df345549","tid":1993760,"uid":270308,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:03:13.000Z","msg":"傳左幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />星島都出左遍文"},{"pid":"ba81dfd58b8d6cad0716babf71af29dd86eae289","tid":1993760,"uid":95499,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:03:42.000Z","msg":"靜雞雞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d149453c33a63247793b8cebdd5ca5291ff5e92","tid":1993760,"uid":302447,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:05:59.000Z","msg":"咁我都幾肯定一定會爆炸<br />\n不過究竟係邊個做就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944a7a408296701c7aedfebca1b004e56e8b77ba","tid":1993760,"uid":678